the-post-formats-ui-feature/">Refonte de l&rsquo;interface des formats d&rsquo;articles</a></li>\n<li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/core/2013/01/07/wordpress-3-6-autosave-and-post-locking/">Refonte des fonctionnalit&eacute;s de sauvegarde automatique et&nbsp;verrouillage&nbsp;lors de l&rsquo;&eacute;dition des contenus</a></li>\n<li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/core/2013/01/07/wordpress-3-6-edit-flow/">Refonte du workflow de publication</a></li>\n<li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/core/2013/01/07/wordpress-3-6-revisions/">Refonte de l&rsquo;interface des r&eacute;visions</a></li>\n<li><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/core/2013/01/08/wordpress-3-6-menus/">Refonte de l&rsquo;interface des menus</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Autrement dit, pas de nouveaut&eacute; majeure, mais simplement la modernisation des fonctionnalit&eacute;s existantes du CMS. Cela est une tr&egrave;s bonne chose concernant le workflow de publication dont l&rsquo;API existante n&rsquo;est pas forc&eacute;ment tr&egrave;s fonctionnelle.</p>\n<p>Si vous voulez contribuer &agrave; WordPress, n&rsquo;attendez plus ;)</p>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"Insidedaweb : 404, Friends not Found (ou Comment Augmenter ses Fans de 354%)";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:238:"http://www.insidedaweb.com/wordpress-seo/referencement-wordpress-seo/404-frie